{"tid":2145165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"官自我覆核改判更生  高院准青年保釋上訴","createTime":"2020-08-08T02:12:31.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T02:31:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"a0b54307fb1513813cb4e00f5020b56691ae90ac","tid":2145165,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:12:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200808/FQE6SRIUNZT5EPUTK3T7BMAL4I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200808%2FFQE6SRIUNZT5EPUTK3T7BMAL4I%2F&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDGFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=a17fc728\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200808%2FFQE6SRIUNZT5EPUTK3T7BMAL4I%2F&h=0a485930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200808/FQE6SRIUNZT5EPUTK3T7BMAL4I/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n官自我覆核改判更生 <br />\n高院准青年保釋上訴<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jL7-YUF2y4Iy13zPmPrA_QJkDdk=/588x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/DW55EWEM4JKI3F6VKDDZEZP2Y4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjL7-YUF2y4Iy13zPmPrA_QJkDdk%3D%2F588x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FDW55EWEM4JKI3F6VKDDZEZP2Y4.jpg&h=d55c164f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n香淑嫻<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】患過度活躍症及專注力不足的18歲中五生，去年11.11大三罷在柴灣被搜出彈簧刀，審訊後被裁定管有違禁武器罪成，還柙候判期間獲高等法院批准保釋。裁判官香淑嫻及後准男生簽保守行為，惟事後稱遭辯方大律師的陳詞誤導，主動覆核刑期後改判男生入更生中心，更拒絕讓他保釋等候上訴。男生昨向高院申請保釋等候上訴，法官張慧玲認為有合理上訴成功機會，批准申請。男生聞言即與母親對望，雙雙哭泣。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n母子庭內喜極而泣<br />\n<br />\n已入住更生中心七天、頭髮已「鏟青」的吳銘揚（18歲），在犯人欄內聽到可獲保釋，即時望向母親；母親則緊合雙手，兩母子對望後喜極而泣。<br />\n<br />\n被告昨續由大律師郭憬憲。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n。。。。。。。。。。。他同月24日獲高院法官潘兆童批准保釋，得以參與校內考試。<br />\n<br />\n香官於6月30日批准吳以1,000元簽保。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n案件編號：HCMA197/20"},{"pid":"ed48a9fabc0d6cba6ff09fc580cc790ac48187e3","tid":2145165,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:35.000Z","msg":"大家要定時定候捐款去 612基金，長期作戰嚟。<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2142357\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2142357</a>"},{"pid":"54802dfbe5faa90ef58e7c6e3047b0c159de2736","tid":2145165,"uid":62842,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:53.000Z","msg":"留名等睇美帝制裁埋呢條紅官 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a305d259e25ee0dbbc5e28289f1fd512d8da5ab","tid":2145165,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:31:25.000Z","msg":"個口咁撚大 為含撚而進化出來？"}]}